OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear and
OL,6,Fsettled evening. However, low cloud
OL,7,Ffrom the North Sea will spread inland
OL,8,Fto cover most of the region by the
OL,9,Fmorning. A moderate northeasterly wind
OL,10,Ffor most, although staying breezier
OL,11,Falong the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FLow cloud will burn back to
OL,14,Fthe coast during the morning to give
OL,15,Fplenty of sunshine for most places
OL,16,Finland. Temperatures around or a
OL,17,Flittle above average. Breezy
OL,18,Fnortheasterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
